"{\"uid\": \"jamaicaobserver.com-2024-08-05-parisolympics-love-air-china-win-badminton-gold\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"PARIS, France (AFP) - China's Huang Yaqiong won Olympic badminton mixed doubles gold on Friday before she was surprised by a marriage proposal from her off-court partner.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 170, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7, \"end\": 13, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9547620046842459, \"rank\": 0.046391225841682295, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 22, \"end\": 27, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.7988411474715832, \"rank\": 0.24699494501688354, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 30, \"end\": 43, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Huang_Yaqiong\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Huang Yaqiong\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Huang_Yaqiong\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Huang_Yaqiong\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Huang and Zheng Siwei claimed the sport's first gold of the Paris Games when they demolished South Korea's Kim Won-ho and Jeong Na-eun 21-8, 21-11 in just 41 minutes.\", \"from\": 172, \"to\": 338, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 182, \"end\": 193, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zheng_Siwei\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Zheng Siwei\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zheng_Siwei\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zheng_Siwei\"}, {\"begin\": 265, \"end\": 276, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea_national_baseball_team\", \"score\": 0.9804262370587448, \"rank\": 0.019828529886703958, \"text\": \"South Korea\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea_national_baseball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea_national_baseball_team\"}, {\"begin\": 279, \"end\": 289, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Won-ho\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kim Won-ho\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Won-ho\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Won-ho\"}, {\"begin\": 294, \"end\": 306, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeong_Na-eun\", \"score\": 0.9999997434952421, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jeong Na-eun\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeong_Na-eun\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeong_Na-eun\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The pair received their medals at La Chapelle Arena and then climbed down off the podium for a victory lap.\", \"from\": 340, \"to\": 447, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Waiting in the far corner was Huang's boyfriend Liu Yuchen, a men's doubles player who won silver in Tokyo three years ago and exited in the group stage in Paris.\", \"from\": 449, \"to\": 611, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 497, \"end\": 507, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liu_Yuchen\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Liu Yuchen\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liu_Yuchen\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liu_Yuchen\"}, {\"begin\": 550, \"end\": 555, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9999999995980033, \"rank\": 3.606295084068715e-10, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}, {\"begin\": 605, \"end\": 610, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999445828978, \"rank\": 5.5417017912723735e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Liu presented Huang with a bunch of flowers before whipping out a ring and getting down on one knee, much to the delight of the Chinese fans packed into the arena.\", \"from\": 613, \"to\": 776, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 741, \"end\": 748, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_people\", \"score\": 0.8867301096406605, \"rank\": 0.10174845547989012, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_people\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Huang said the proposal had been \\\"very surprising\\\".\", \"from\": 778, \"to\": 829, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I had been preparing for the match,\\\" said the 30-year-old, showing off her ring to reporters.\", \"from\": 831, \"to\": 925, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Today I became an Olympic champion and I got engaged.\", \"from\": 927, \"to\": 981, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I think the ring fits my finger really well.\\\"\", \"from\": 982, \"to\": 1027, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"China's Huang Yaqiong and her off-court partner Liu Yuchen pose for a photo after their engagement.\", \"from\": 1029, \"to\": 1128, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1029, \"end\": 1034, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.7988411474715832, \"rank\": 0.24699494501688354, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1037, \"end\": 1050, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Huang_Yaqiong\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Huang Yaqiong\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Huang_Yaqiong\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Huang_Yaqiong\"}, {\"begin\": 1077, \"end\": 1087, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liu_Yuchen\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Liu Yuchen\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liu_Yuchen\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liu_Yuchen\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(Photo: Badminton World Federation Instagram)  Huang and Zheng stormed into an early lead and took the first game in less than 20 minutes.\", \"from\": 1129, \"to\": 1267, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1186, \"end\": 1191, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zheng_Jie\", \"score\": 0.9999999997621671, \"rank\": 1.2315270956216793e-10, \"text\": \"Zheng\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zheng_Jie\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zheng_Jie\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The South Korean pair made a better start to the second game but their Chinese opponents were relentless, closing out the match when Jeong hit a return wide.\", \"from\": 1269, \"to\": 1426, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1279, \"end\": 1285, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hangul\", \"score\": 0.9949623758113573, \"rank\": 0.005042854776512499, \"text\": \"Korean\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hangul\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hangul\"}, {\"begin\": 1340, \"end\": 1347, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_people\", \"score\": 0.8867301096406605, \"rank\": 0.10174845547989012, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_people\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Zheng and Huang lost in the fina